examples.en: Wherein lies the difference between conservatism and liberalism?

examples.en: He espouses a kind of ultra conservatism that even some members of his own party cannot support.

examples.en: When the winds suddenly shifted on social values, the weathercocks wasted no time in proclaiming their newfound passion for conservatism.
